  "title": "Telemarketer - WFH | 5 days - $2.2k + Comm [0580]",
  "description": "<p>Working hours: Mon – Fri, 10am – 6pm<br />Location: Work from home (WFH)<br />Salary: $1800 - $2200 + Commission</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct outbound telemarketing calls for banking-related products and services</li><li>Introduce and explain banking products clearly and professionally</li><li>Identify customer needs and qualify potential leads</li><li>Set appointments or refer interested customers to relationship managers / sales team</li><li>Follow up with warm leads when required</li><li>Maintain accurate records of calls, responses, and outcomes</li><li>Achieve daily and monthly call and lead targets</li><li>Comply with company policies and basic banking compliance guidelines</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Min 1 year of relevant experience</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
